  "bio_raw": "Fatema Khan is currently working as a Lecturer in the Department of Computer Science and Engineering (CSE) at University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh (ULAB). She pursued her M.Sc and B.Sc. in Computer Science and Engineering from Jahangirnagar University, Bangladesh. Previously, she worked as a full-time Lecturer in the department of CSE at Green University of Bangladesh for 1 year. Her research interests are Machine Learning and Natural Language Processing.",
